{"tid":2127453,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為連登首席美斯迷，咁多年以來其實好眼紅C朗","createTime":"2020-07-27T10:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T14:19:42.000Z","uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a4dc76cbc036b995114d2ce09494494dfbe194a","tid":2127453,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:32:35.000Z","msg":"作為連登首席美斯迷，咁多年以來其實好眼紅C朗。<br />\n<br />\n首先論樣貌，我美斯輸左一截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nC朗有既除左男FANS外，仲有一堆唔太識波既女FANS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當年仲有一班曼聯死忠撐朗，有唔少仲好Q靚。<br />\n佢個樣就算唔踢波，搞廣告搞娛樂拍電影都好過好多明星，食個樣都可以一世無憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我美斯FANS追蹤數都少左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就到身形，<br />\n我美斯技術好又點，天生有侏儒症，要長期打針先係得呢個高度。<br />\n呢個病，限制左美斯好多踢法，令佢做唔到一個全能既前鋒。學C朗用頭入波果D真係冇乜可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nC朗仲要操到咁FIT，老過我美斯咁多，今年表現仲可以好過佢。我地真係好眼紅C朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdda733bb537aef53ea0075b91a91c88fbbc5c8","tid":2127453,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"再講就到個人榮耀。作為美斯迷真係好眼紅佢攞咁多。<br />\n點解C朗可以入到皇馬，有咁多好隊友，世界級中場摩迪，攞歐聯比我美斯多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起歐聯次數我真係好傷心，我美斯永遠會俾人扣兩次，<br />\n因為有一年，我美斯只係踢過一場外圍賽就坐後備到棒杯。<br />\n仲有一年，北京電視機講到成行成市，呢一點我都冇得駁，當晚判罰真心有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我真係好眼紅C朗有咁多歐聯<br />\n而自己果隊，隊友同教練永遠都唔上力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年年俾人反CAP，輸完垃圾羅馬又輸賤種利記，點解我美斯付出咁多，回報永遠都咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然年年西甲都屌打，但佢地都有幾年贏過，冇得零封C朗榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再講就係國家隊榮耀，<br />\n明明有好幾年已經叫緊糊，我地連登高登時期已經講話美斯攞咗國家隊榮耀就係球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌啦星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，年年畀人截糊，好好地一隊阿根廷，曾經有八年係全球三甲球隊。竟然多次臨門撻q，得第二名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最慘就係，竟然俾一直競爭對手C朗屎忽撞棍，歐國杯贏左國家隊榮譽先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明葡萄牙國家隊垃圾到冇人有，竟然執雞成功贏左世界杯冠軍陣容法國。<br />\n<br />\n對上果年仲贏Q埋歐國聯冠軍，兩個國家隊榮耀係手。<br />\n<br />\n佢做左葡萄牙英雄，而我美斯係阿根廷仲要畀馬勒當拿嘲諷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解佢C朗就係英雄，我係美斯就狗熊，我真係好撚眼紅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bdb4e23d474c75d49ea264fd6441c3eac3b97e","tid":2127453,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"你點作"},{"pid":"20a1d4ccd7f20c60e5502c44bf920fcafca2e388","tid":2127453,"uid":38737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"你點眼紅的"},{"pid":"038a11cc5796de2508b2b5512098dffcbd052de6","tid":2127453,"uid":72405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"你點眼紅的"},{"pid":"b830524ac110d8699d0f548f4f61577e91ad5be0","tid":2127453,"uid":45498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"你點眼紅的"},{"pid":"97a68c040c68f527905cda29feac1c6c35ce6b28","tid":2127453,"uid":199227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-