,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"你點作的？"},{"pid":"5f2308e918957143f285f6dc1411819f8668db69","tid":2127453,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"唔怪得要做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快個監躉又黎人形蜈蚣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf281dd59b5085408a6788aeaa40e2d843cf65c","tid":2127453,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"你點紅的"},{"pid":"56c19ce6aa15056340e18a60ccfb6b8f986ecc8c","tid":2127453,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16757825e0f9df71b65f8946bd7a551d81eb8d20","tid":2127453,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44e4e415e8a90a78a08391e94319f34a65f6de8f","tid":2127453,"uid":340189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"你點作的？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"冇作到真心眼紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c56191f891a14635c3f4a3803290b4556b653d","tid":2127453,"uid":313905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"你點紅㗎？"},{"pid":"ad0bd08bab644918b17a19a4c89085f0a1feb171","tid":2127453,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vCK9W8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvCK9W8b.jpg&h=096d8f14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b51dd8ee56e4185a665ec04d7ad1113732d23e8","tid":2127453,"uid":63152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:19:42.000Z","msg":"打咁多廢話 你返去同活狗李狗人型蜈蚣算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}